    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 assessment plan. Experimental comparison yields MAE 8.3% against the 15% criterion, and RH < 1 for all worst-case operating points. The credibility assessment supports use of the CFD model for the stated COU. The claim that the model adequately predicts worst-case hemolysis operating conditions is considered substantiated by the totality of validation evidence reviewed by the assessment team.",
